<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CEEDF113DF93BA35753C1A964958260" class="external free" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CEEDF113DF93BA35753C1A964958260" rel="nofollow">http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CEEDF113DF93BA35753C1A964958260</a></li>
